SELF
TRAPPING
OF
AN
ELECTRON
BY
THE
ACOUSTICAL
MODE
OF
LATTICE
VIBRATION
WHEN
THE
COUPLING
CONSTANT
BETWEEN
THE
ELECTRON
AND
ACOUSTIC
MODE
VIBRATION
EXCEEDS
A
CRITICAL
VALUE
THE
EFFECTIVE
